<!-- Short description of the student shop
-->

<h2  class="ss_head">Physics &amp; Astronomy Student Machine Shop (SMS)</h2>
<div class="ss_intro">
<p text-align="left"> 
The department of Physics & Astronomy provides a machine shop for use by
students, staff & faculty.  Prior to use, everyone must complete a course 
on the working of the SMS & safety (signup below).
</p>
<p>
The Student Shop is open to qualified users   Monday to Friday:  < 08:00 - 16:00 >
</p>
<p>
Every SMS user <strong>MUST</strong> comply with the
<a href="http://gamma.phas.ubc.ca/sms/sms_safety_v01.pdf">SMS safety regulations</a> [PDF] .
</p>
<p>
If you wish to use the SMS, submit the following form for the 'SMS training course'  &
please read the <a href="http://gamma.phas.ubc.ca/sms/sms_handbook_01_v01.pdf">
handbook for the course</a>.
</p>
</div>
